SUMMARY:Ramble On: EDE Rocks!
DESCRIPTION:The Evanston Dance Ensemble is diving into the archives! Join us as we explore the culture\, attitude\, and expansive reach of rock and roll music. Artistic Director Enid Smith and Assistant to the Director Macala Bartucci are joined by guests Kaleigh Dent\, Julie Cartier\, Tori Isaac\, Ro Goodman\, and EDE founding director Béa Rashid in this electrifying evening of dance. \nWhen: March 19\, 7:30p | March 20\, 7:30p | March 21\, 10a Relaxed Performance | March 21\, 1p | March 22\, 1p |\nWhere: Josephine Louis Theater\, Northwestern University\, 20 Arts Circle Dr.\, Evanston\, IL 60208\nInfo: (847) 491-7282 or https://www.evanstondanceensemble.org/performances-tickets
URL:https://evanstonmade.org/event/ramble-on-ede-rocks/
LOCATION:jospehine lewis\, Josephine Louis Theater\, Northwestern University\, 20 Arts Circle Dr.\, Evanston\, IL\, 60208\, United States
